{
  "id": "69a300c0a7b9068792c21e40",
  "title": "魔法使いだったら自分は何属性だと思うか",
  "created": 1772290241,
  "updated": 1774550036,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a300c0a7b9068792c21e40",
      "text": "魔法使いだったら自分は何属性だと思うか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772290241
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f40",
      "text": "from [2026/02/28]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772290241
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f41",
      "text": "魔法使いだったら自分は何属性だと思うか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772290241
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f42",
      "text": " 火🔥[caki.icon][sta.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772375193
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f43",
      "text": " 風🌪️[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772339977
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f44",
      "text": " 土🌱[kumoridai.icon]",
      "userId": "68afcc9b93f1844fed9e3b89",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772298021
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f45",
      "text": " 水💧[HelloPeople.icon][koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772419990
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f46",
      "text": " 光🌟",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772290241
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f47",
      "text": " 闇🌚[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772365959
    },
    {
      "id": "69a300c00000000000b56f48",
      "text": "　雷⛈️[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772290241,
      "updated": 1772292073
    },
    {
      "id": "69a38d1e000000000082d164",
      "text": "　雪❄[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772326174,
      "updated": 1772326195
    },
    {
      "id": "69a398dc00000000005faf7b",
      "text": "　木🌲[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1772329181,
      "updated": 1772329194
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1cb0000000000d67655",
      "text": "　山🏔",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772335557,
      "updated": 1772335567
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1d50000000000d67656",
      "text": "　正+",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772335568,
      "updated": 1772335575
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1dc0000000000d67657",
      "text": "　負-",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772335575,
      "updated": 1772335579
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1e00000000000d67659",
      "text": "　虚i[baku3.icon]",
      "userId": "6970e90c94fe766b6a026352",
      "created": 1772335579,
      "updated": 1774550036
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1f50000000000d6765b",
      "text": "　無",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772335600,
      "updated": 1772335601
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45de50000000000588145",
      "text": "　聖✝",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772379622,
      "updated": 1772379640
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45dff0000000000588146",
      "text": "　混沌🌀",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772379647,
      "updated": 1772379666
    },
    {
      "id": "69a38f1d0000000000542efd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772326685,
      "updated": 1772326685
    },
    {
      "id": "69a44cf20000000000714b9e",
      "text": "理由欄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772375283,
      "updated": 1772375289
    },
    {
      "id": "69a38f1d0000000000542efe",
      "text": " 土に憧れがあるけど友人には火だと言われるし自分でもそう思う[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772326685,
      "updated": 1772326737
    },
    {
      "id": "69a44cf90000000000714b9f",
      "text": " 激情的だからなぁ🔥[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772375290,
      "updated": 1772375290
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45b4d0000000000e863c8",
      "text": " 激情的なうえにこだわりが強いから雷🌩️[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772378958,
      "updated": 1772397328
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4794b00000000004e2829",
      "text": "　 1. 一つ一つの投射先が狭く、局所的・選択的。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772386635,
      "updated": 1772394225
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4975b0000000000d9d53c",
      "text": "　 2. 電気やけどは表面に傷跡がない場合にも深部が損傷していることがあり、通常のやけどに比べて治療が厄介",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772394331,
      "updated": 1772394335
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a31b00000000009ec63c",
      "text": "　 \t自分は他者への心理的影響について鈍感なところがある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772397339,
      "updated": 1772397451
    },
    {
      "id": "69a497660000000000d9d53f",
      "text": "　 3. 大気の状態が悪いことを前提とする。言い換えると、周辺的な被害と副作用がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772394343,
      "updated": 1772394344
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a34d00000000009ec63d",
      "text": "　 \t場の負の感情を吸収する。また、自身の不機嫌な気分を伝染させる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772397389,
      "updated": 1772397441
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45b610000000000e863c9",
      "text": "　 4. 炎もプラズマだが、こちらは電磁気力が発生する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772378977,
      "updated": 1772394808
    },
    {
      "id": "69a47b7100000000004e282d",
      "text": "　 \t発電がそのまま活力に直結する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772387186,
      "updated": 1772394296
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a3fa00000000009ec63e",
      "text": "　 \t\t[/ この点では闇に近いか]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772397563,
      "updated": 1772397576
    },
    {
      "id": "69a497050000000000d9d538",
      "text": "　 \t電磁気力は重力よりも強力に星間ガスを集積させるが、惑星大の天体への影響は少ない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772394246,
      "updated": 1772397610
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45c180000000000e863cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772379161,
      "updated": 1772379161
    },
    {
      "id": "69a393bc000000000082d166",
      "text": "属性のない魔法もありそう [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772327868,
      "updated": 1772328503
    },
    {
      "id": "69a307da0000000000e7ad20",
      "text": " 数魔術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772292059,
      "updated": 1772328834
    },
    {
      "id": "69a45e1b0000000000588147",
      "text": " 青魔道士になりたい[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772379676,
      "updated": 1772379695
    },
    {
      "id": "69a393da000000000082d167",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772327899,
      "updated": 1772327899
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3960e000000000082d168",
      "text": "魔法かどうか微妙なもの",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328463,
      "updated": 1772328500
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3966f000000000082d16c",
      "text": " 占星術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328559,
      "updated": 1772328841
    },
    {
      "id": "69a39610000000000082d169",
      "text": "　降霊術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328465,
      "updated": 1772328849
    },
    {
      "id": "69a39648000000000082d16b",
      "text": "　錬金術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328520,
      "updated": 1772328860
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3963e000000000082d16a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328510,
      "updated": 1772328510
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3970e000000000082d172",
      "text": "参照",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328719,
      "updated": 1772328724
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3bf340000000000a85e6d",
      "text": " [世界観]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772338997,
      "updated": 1772339007
    },
    {
      "id": "69a39679000000000082d16d",
      "text": " [善悪二元論]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328569,
      "updated": 1772328727
    },
    {
      "id": "69a39684000000000082d16e",
      "text": " [三位一体説]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328581,
      "updated": 1772328727
    },
    {
      "id": "69a39696000000000082d16f",
      "text": " [四元素説]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328598,
      "updated": 1772328727
    },
    {
      "id": "69a396dc000000000082d171",
      "text": " [五行説]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772328669,
      "updated": 1772328727
